column2: SELECT               s.specObjID AS id, s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.ra AS ra, s.dec AS dec,              s.z AS redshift, s.zErr AS redshift_err, s.sn_# AS snr,             spp.feha AS Fe_H, spp.fehaerr AS Fe_H_err,              spp.teffa AS T_eff, spp.teffaerr AS T_eff_err,             spp.logga AS log_g, spp.loggaerr AS log_g_err,             spp.alphafe AS a_Fe, spp.alphafeerr AS a_Fe_err,             p.psfMag_r AS mag, p.psfMagErr_r AS mag_err,             p.psfMag_u AS mag_u, p.psfMagErr_u AS mag_u_err,             p.psfMag_g AS mag_g, p.psfMagErr_g AS mag_g_err,             p.psfMag_r AS mag_r, p.psfMagErr_r AS mag_r_err,             p.psfMag_i AS mag_i, p.psfMagErr_i AS mag_i_err,             p.psfMag_z AS mag_z, p.psfMagErr_z AS mag_z_err         FROM SpecObj s             INNER JOIN sppParams spp ON spp.specobjID = s.specObjID             INNER JOIN PhotoObj p ON p.objID = s.bestObjID         WHERE specClass = # AND zConf > #                AND p.psfMag_r > #               -- exclude unmeasured psf mag                         ORDER BY s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID
